quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  24,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  24,1,"yeh ( aik ) sourat hai jis ko hum ne nazilkiya aur is ( ke ehkaam ) ko farz kar diya, aur is mein wazeh المطالب ayatain nazil kee taakay tum yaad rakho"
  24,2,badkaari karne wali aurat aur badkaari karne wala mard ( jab un ki badkaari saabit hojaye to ) dono mein se har aik ko so daray maro. aur agar tum khuda aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhtay ho to shara khuda ( ke hukum ) mein tumhe un par hargiz taras nah aeye. aur chahiye ke un ki saza ke waqt musalmanoon ki aik jamaat bhi mojood ho
  24,3,badkaar mard to badkaar ya mushriq aurat ke siwa nikah nahi karta aur badkaar aurat ko bhi badkaar ya mushriq mard ke siwa aur koi nikah mein nahi lata aur yeh ( yani badkaar aurat se nikah karna ) mominon par haraam hai
  24,4,aur jo log parhaizgaar aurton ko badkaari ka aib lagayen aur is par chaar gawah nah layein to un ko isi daray maro aur kabhi un ki shahadat qubool nah karo. aur yahi badkirdar hain
  24,5,haan jo is ke baad tauba karlen aur ( apni haalat ) sanwaar len to khuda ( bhi ) bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  24,6,aur jo log apni aurton par badkaari ki tohmat lagayen aur khud un ke siwa un ke gawah nah hon to har aik ki shahadat yeh hai ke pehlay to chaar baar khuda ki qasam khaye ke be shak woh sacha hai
  24,7,aur panchwin baar yeh ( kahe ) ke agar woh jhoota ho to is par khuda ki laanat
  24,8,aur aurat se saza ko yeh baat taall sakti hai ke woh pehlay chaar baar khuda ki qasam khaye ke be shak yeh jhoota hai
  24,9,aur panchwin dafaa yun ( kahe ) ke agar yeh sacha ho to mujh par khuda ka ghazab ( nazil ho )
  24,10,aur agar tum par khuda ka fazl aur is ki meharbani nah hoti to bohat si kharabian peda hojatin. magar woh sahib karam hai aur yeh ke khuda tauba qubool karne wala hakeem hai
  24,11,jin logon ne bohtan baandha hai tum hi mein se aik jamaat hai is ko apne haq mein bura nah samjhna. balkay woh tumahray liye acha hai. un mein se jis shakhs ne gunah ka jitna hissa liya is ke liye itna hi wabaal hai. aur jis ne un mein se is bohtan ka bara boojh uthaya hai is ko bara azaab hoga
  24,12,jab tum ne woh baat suni thi to momin mardon aur aurton ne kyun apne dilon mein naik gumaan nahkiya. aur kyun nah kaha ke yeh Sarih tufaan hai
  24,13,yeh ( iftira pardaaz ) apni baat ( ki tasdeeq ) ke ( liye ) chaar gawah kyun nah laaye. to jab yeh gawah nahi laske to khuda ke nazdeek yahi jhutay hain
  24,14,aur agar duniya aur akhirat mein tum par khuda ka fazl aur is ki rehmat nah hoti to jis baat ka tum charcha karte they is ki wajah se tum par bara ( sakht ) azaab nazil hota
  24,15,jab tum apni zabanon se is ka aik dosray se zikar karte they aur apne munh se aisi baat kehte they jis ka tum ko kuch ilm nah tha aur tum usay aik halki baat samajte they aur khuda ke nazdeek woh barri bhaari baat thi
  24,16,aur jab tum ne usay suna tha to kyun nah keh diya ke hamein Shayaan nahi ke aisi baat zabaan par nah layein. ( perwar-digaar ) to pak hai yeh to ( bohat ) bara bohtan hai
  24,17,khuda tumhe nasiyaat karta hai ke agar momin ho to phir kabhi aisa kaam nah karna
  24,18,aur khuda tumahray ( samjhane ke liye ) apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan farmata hai. aur khuda jan-nay wala hikmat wala hai
  24,19,aur jo log is baat ko pasand karte hain ke mominon mein be hiyai yani ( tohmat badkaari ki khabar ) phailay un ko duniya aur akhirat mein dukh dainay wala azaab hoga. aur khuda jaanta hai aur tum nahi jantay
  24,20,aur agar tum par khuda ka fazl aur is ki rehmat nah hoti ( tokiya kuch nah hota magar woh kareem hai ) aur yeh ke khuda nihayat meharban aur Raheem hai
  24,21,ae momino! shetan ke qadmon par nah chalna. aur jo shakhs shetan ke qadmon par chalay ga to shetan to be hiyai ( ki baatein ) aur buray kaam hi betaye ga. aur agar tum par khuda ka fazl aur is ki meharbani nah hoti to 1 shakhs bhi tum mein pak nah ho sakta. magar khuda jis ko chahta hai pak kardaita hai. aur khuda suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
  24,22,"aur jo log tum mein sahib fazl ( aur sahib ) wusat hain, woh is baat ki qasam nah khayen ke rishta daaron aur mohtajon aur watan chore jaane walon ko kuch kharch paat nahi den ge. un ko chahiye ke maaf kar dein aur dar guzar karen.kiya tum pasand nahi karte ke khuda tum ko bakhash day? aur khuda to bakhsnay wala meharban hai"
  24,23,jo log parhaizgaar aur buray kamon se be khabar aur imaan daar aurton par badkaari ki tohmat lagatay hain un par duniya o akhrat ( dono ) mein laanat hai. aur un ko sakht azaab hoga
  24,24,( yani qayamat ke roz ) jis din un ki zubanain haath aur paon sab un ke kamon ki gawahi den ge
  24,25,is din khuda un ko ( un ke aamaal ka ) poora poora ( aur ) theek badla day ga aur un ko maloom hojaye ga ke khuda barhaq ( aur haq ko ) zahir karne wala hai
  24,26,napak aurtain napak mardon ke liye aur napak mard napak aurton ke liye. aur pak aurtain pak mardon ke liye. aur pak mard pak aurton ke liye. yeh ( pak log ) un ( badgoiyon ) ki baton se buri hain ( aur ) un ke liye bakhshish aur naik rozi hai
  24,27,momino! apne gharon ke siwa dosray ( logon ke ) gharon mein ghar walon se ijazat liye aur un ko salam kiye baghair daakhil nah howa karo. yeh tumahray haq mein behtar hai ( aur hum ) yeh nasiyaat is liye karte hain ke shayad tum yaad rakho
  24,28,agar tum ghar mein kisi ko mojood nah pao to jab taq tum ko ijazat nah di jaye is mein mat daakhil ho. aur agar yeh kaha jaye ke ( is waqt ) lout jao to lout jaya karo. yeh tumahray liye barri pakizgee ki baat hai. aur jo kaam tum karte ho khuda sab jaanta hai
  24,29,"haan agar tum kisi aisay makaan mein jao jis mein koi nah basta ho aur is mein tumhara asbaab ( rakha ) ho, tum par kuch gunah nahi, aur jo kuch tum zahir karte ho aur jo posheeda karte ho khuda ko sab maloom hai"
  24,30,momin mardon se keh do ke apni nazrain neechi rakha karen aur apni sharam gaahon ki hifazatkiya karen. yeh un ke liye barri pakizgee ki baat hai aur jo kaam yeh karte hain khuda un se khabardaar hai
  24,31,aur momin aurton se bhi keh do ke woh bhi apni nigehain neechi rakha karen aur apni sharam gaahon ki hifazatkiya karen aur apni Araish ( yani zewar ke maqamat ) ko zahir nah honay diya karen magar jo un mein se khula rehta ho. aur apne seenon par اوڑھنیاں oorhay raha karen aur apne khawand aur baap aur khsr aur baityon aur khawand ke beton aur bhaiyon aur bhtijyon aur bhanjon aur apni ( hi qisam ki ) aurton aur londi ghulamoo ke siwa neez un Khudam ke jo aurton ki khwahish nah rakhen ya aisay larkoon ke jo aurton ke parday ki cheezon se waaqif nah hon ( gharz un logon ke siwa ) kisi par apni zeenat ( aur singaar ke maqamat ) ko zahir nah honay den. aur apne paon ( aisay tor se zameen par ) nah marain ( ke jhankaar kaanon mein puhanche aur ) un ka posheeda zewar maloom hojaye. aur momino! sab khuda ke agay tauba karo taakay Falah pao
  24,32,aur apni qoum ki bewa aurton ke nikah kardiya karo. aur apne ghulamoo aur londion ke bhi jo naik hon ( nikah kardiya karo ) agar woh muflis hon ge to khuda un ko apne fazl se khush haal kardey ga. aur khuda ( bohat ) wusat wala aur ( sab kuch ) jan-nay wala hai
  24,33,aur jin ko bayah ka Maqdoor nah ho woh pak damni ko ikhtiyar kiye rahen yahan taq ke khuda un ko apne fazl se ghanni kardey. aur jo ghulam tum se makatbat chahain agar tum un mein ( salahiyat aur ) neki pao to un se mukatbat karlo. aur khuda ne jo maal tum ko bakhsha hai is mein se un ko bhi do. aur apni londion ko agar woh pak daman rehna chahain to ( be sharmi se ) dunyawi zindagi ke fawaid haasil karne ke liye badkaari par majaboor nah karna. aur jo un ko majaboor kere ga to un ( bechariyon ) ke majaboor kiye jaane ke baad khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  24,34,aur hum ne tumhari taraf roshan ayatain nazil ki hain aur jo log tum se pehlay guzar chuke hain un ki khabrain aur parhaiz garon ke liye nasiyaat
  24,35,khuda asmano aur zameen ka noor hai. is ke noor ki misaal aisi hai ke goya aik taaq hai jis mein chairag hai. aur chairag aik Qandil mein hai. aur Qandil ( aisi saaf shafaaf hai ke ) goya moti ka sa chamakta howa rarah hai is mein aik mubarak darakht ka tail jalaya jata hai ( yani ) Zaitoon ke nah mashriq ki taraf hai nah maghrib ki taraf. ( aisa maloom hota hai ke ) is ka tail khuwa aag usay nah bhi chovay julne ko tayyar hai ( pari ) roshni par roshni ( ho rahi hai ) khuda apne noor se jis ko chahta hai seedhi raah dekhata hai. aur khuda ne ( jo misalein ) bayan farmata hai ( to ) logon ke ( samjhane ke ) liye aur khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  24,36,( woh Qandil ) un gharon mein ( hai ) jin ke baray mein khuda ne irshad farmaya hai ke buland kiye jayen aur wahan khuda ke naam ka zikarkiya jaye ( aur ) un mein subah vsham is ki tasbeeh karte rahen
  24,37,( yani aisay ) log jin ko khuda ke zikar aur namaz parhnay aur zakaat dainay se nah sodagari ghaafil karti hai nah khareed vfrokht. woh is din se jab dil ( khauf aur ghabrahat ke sabab ) ulat jayen ge aur ankhen ( oopar ko charh jayen gi ) drtay hain
  24,38,taakay khuda un ko un ke amlon ka bohat acha badla day aur apne fazl se ziyada bhi ataa kere. aur jis ko chahta hai khuda be shumaar rizaq deta hai
  24,39,jin logon ne kufarkiya un ke aamaal ki misaal aisi hai jaisay maidan mein rait ke piyasa usay pani samjhay yahan taq ke jab is ke paas aeye to usay kuch bhi nah paye aur khuda hi ko apne paas dekhe to woh usay is ka hisaab poora poora chuka day. aur khuda jald hisaab karne wala hai
  24,40,"ya ( un ke aamaal ki misaal aisi hai ) jaisay dareaye ameeq mein andheray jis par lehar charhi chali aati ho aur is ke oopar aur lehar ( aa rahi ho ) aur is ke oopar baadal ho, gharz andheray hi andheray hon, aik par aik ( chaaya howa ) jab apna haath nikalay to kuch nah dekh sakay. aur jis ko khuda roshni nah day is ko ( kahin bhi ) roshni nahi ( mil sakti )"
  24,41,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke jo log asmano aur zameen mein hain khuda ki tasbeeh karte hain aur par phelaaye hue janwar bhi. aur sab apni namaz aur tasbeeh ke tareeqay se waaqif hain. aur jo kuch woh karte hain ( sab ) khuda ko maloom hai
  24,42,aur aasman aur zameen ki badshahi khuda ke liye hai. aur khuda hi ki taraf lout kar jana hai
  24,43,"kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke khuda hi baadalon ko chalata hai, aur un ko aapas mein mila deta hai, phir un ko teh bah teh kardaita hai, phir tum dekhte ho ke baadal mein se meen nikal ( kar baras ) raha hai aur aasman mein jo ( oloon ke ) pahar hain, un se olley nazil karta hai to jis par chahta hai is ko barsa deta hai aur jis se chahta hai hata deta hai. aur baadal mein jo bijli hoti hai is ki chamak aankhon ko Khaira karkay benaye ko achke liye jati hai"
  24,44,aur khuda hi raat aur din ko badalta rehta hai. ahal Basarat ke liye is mein barri Ibrat hai
  24,45,"aur khuda hi ne har chalne phirnay walay jandaar ko pani se pedakiya. to is mein baazay aisay hain ke pait ke bil chaltay hain aur baaz aisay hain jo do paon par chaltay hain aur baaz aisay hain jo chaar paon par chaltay hain. khuda jo chahta hai peda karta hai, be shak khuda har cheez par Qadir hai"
  24,46,hum hi ne roshan ayatain nazil kee hain aur khuda jis ko chahta hai seedhay raste ki taraf Hadayat karta hai
  24,47,aur baaz log kehte hain ke hum khuda par aur rasool par imaan laaye aur ( un ka ) hukum maan liya phir is ke baad un mein se aik firqa phir jata hai aur yeh log sahib imaan hi nahi hain
  24,48,aur jab un ko khuda aur is ke rasool ki taraf bulaya jata hai taakay ( rasool khuda ) un ka qazia chuka den to un mein se aik firqa munh phair laita hai
  24,49,agar ( maamla ) haq ( ho aur ) un ko ( pohanchana ) ho to un ki taraf Mutee ho kar chalay atay hain
  24,50,kiya un ke dilon mein bemari hai ya ( yeh ) shak mein hain ya un ko yeh khauf hai ke khuda aur is ka rasool un ke haq mein zulm karen ge ( nahi ) balkay yeh khud zalim hain
  24,51,mominon ki to yeh baat hai ke jab khuda aur is ke rasool ki taraf bulaye jayen taakay woh un mein faisla karen to kahin ke hum ne ( hukum ) sun liya aur maan liya. aur yahi log Falah panay walay hain
  24,52,aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmabardari kere ga aur is se daray ga to aisay log morad ko pounchanay walay hain
  24,53,"aur ( yeh ) khuda ki sakht sakht kasmain khatay hain ke agar tum un ko hukum do to ( sab gharon se ) nikal kharray hon. keh do ke kasmain mat khao, pasandeeda farmabardari ( darkaar hai ). be shak khuda tumahray sab aamaal se khabardaar hai"
  24,54,keh do ke khuda ki farmabardari karo aur rasool khuda ke hukum par chalo. agar munh morron ge to rasool par ( is cheez ka ada karna ) jo un ke zimmay hai aur tum par ( is cheez ka ada karna ) hai jo tumahray zimmay hai aur agar tum un ke farmaan par chalo ge to seedha rasta palo ge aur rasool ke zimmay to saaf saaf ( ehkaam khuda ka ) pouncha dena hai
  24,55,jo log tum mein se imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay un se khuda ka wada hai ke un ko malik ka haakim banade ga jaissa un se pehlay logon ko haakim banaya tha aur un ke deen ko jisay is ne un ke liye pasandkiya hai mustahkam o paidaar kere ga aur khauf ke baad un ko aman bakhshay ga. woh meri ibadat karen ge aur mere sath kisi cheez ko shareek nah banayen ge. aur jo is ke baad kufar kere to aisay log badkirdar hain
  24,56,aur namaz parhte raho aur zakaat dete raho aur paighambar khuda ke farmaan par chaltay raho taakay tum par rehmat ki jaye
  24,57,aur aisa khayaal nah karna ke tum par kafir log ghalib ajayeen ge ( woh ja hi kahan satke hain ) un ka thikana dozakh hai aur woh bohat bura thikana hai
  24,58,momino! tumahray ghulam londiyan aur jo bachay tum mein se balogh ko nahi puhanche teen dafaa yani ( teen auqaat mein ) tum se ijazat liya karen. ( aik to ) namaz subah se pehlay aur ( dosray garmi ki dopehar ko ) jab tum kapray utaar dete ho. aur teesray esha ki namaz ke baad. ( yeh ) teen ( waqt ) tumahray parday ( ke ) hain un ke ( agay ) peechay ( yani dosray waqton mein ) nah tum par kuch gunah hai aur nah un par. ke kaam kaaj ke liye aik dosray ke paas atay rehtay ho. is terhan khuda apni ayatain tum se khol khol kar bayan farmata hai aur khuda bara ilm wala aur bara hikmat wala hai
  24,59,aur jab tumahray larke baaligh ho jaien to un ko bhi isi terhan ijazat leni chahiye jis terhan un se aglay ( yani barray aadmi ) ijazat haasil karte rahay hain. is terhan khuda tum se apni ayatain khol khol kar sunataa hai. aur khuda jan-nay wala aur hikmat wala hai
  24,60,"aur barri Umar ki aurtain jin ko nikah ki tawaqqa nahi rahi, aur woh kapray utaar kar sir nanga karliya karen to un par kuch gunah nahi bashart e kay apni zeenat ki cheezein nah zahir karen. aur is se bhi bachchen to yeh un ke haq mein behtar hai. aur khuda santa aur jaanta hai"
  24,61,nah to andhay par kuch gunah hai aur nah lngrhe par aur nah bemaar par aur nah khud tum par ke apne gharon se khana khao ya apne bapon ke gharon se ya apni maaon ke gharon se ya bhaiyon ke gharon se ya apni behnoon ke gharon se ya apne chchaon ke gharon se ya apni پھوپھیوں ke gharon se ya apne mamoon ke gharon se ya apni khalaaon ke gharon se ya is ghar se jis ki knjyan tumahray haath mein hon ya apne doston ke gharon se ( aur is ka bhi ) tum par kuch gunah nahi ke sab mil kar khana khao ya judda judda. aur jab gharon mein jaya karo to apne ( ghar walon ko ) salamkiya karo. ( yeh ) khuda ki taraf se mubarak aur pakeeza tohfa hai. is terhan khuda apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan farmata hai taakay tum samjhoo
  24,62,momin to woh hain jo khuda par aur is ke rasool par imaan laaye aur jab kabhi aisay kaam ke liye jo jama ho kar karne ka ho paighambar khuda ke paas jama hon to un se ijazat liye baghair chalay nahi jatay. ae paighambar jo log tum se ijazat haasil karte hain wohi khuda par aur is ke rasool par imaan rakhtay hain. so jab yeh log tum se kisi kaam ke liye ijazat manga karen to un mein se jisay chaha karo ijazat day diya karo aur un ke liye khuda se bakhshishen manga karo. kuch shak nahi ke khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  24,63,momino paighambar ke bulanay ko aisa khayaal nah karna jaissa tum aapas mein aik dosray ko bulatay ho. be shak khuda ko yeh log maloom hain jo tum mein se aankhh bacha kar chal dete hain to jo log un ke hukum ki mukhalfat karte hain un ko darna chahiye ke ( aisa nah ho ke ) un par koi aafat par jaye ya takleef dainay wala azaab nazil ho
  24,64,dekho jo kuch asmano aur zameen mein hai sab khuda hi ka hai. jis ( tareeq ) par tum ho woh usay jaanta hai. aur jis roz log is ki taraf lout’tay jayen ge to jo log amal karte rahay woh un ko bta day ga. aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai .
